WorkItem.ClosedComment: This is normal behavior for the optimizer if the values aren't that far off from each other. If the values of change are significant, then please reopen and attach your character file where this happens. Before attaching it, save the item sets the Optimizer is generating into the character file (there's a button on the results pane to do this).
